				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Chu-h%C3%A0nh-nh%E1%BA%ADp-H%C6%B0ng-Y%C3%AAn/poem-Yt_I5MBaX3WLLNGGmUXMtA">Chu hành nhập Hưng Yên - 舟行入興安</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/%C4%90%C3%A0m-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-U3U2GgypqwInGrz_A0LJJw">Đàm Châu - 潭州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C4%83n/%C4%90%C3%A0o-hoa-%C4%91%C3%A0m-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A3n-ca/poem-ebQdjG0QmgBL2Lf0ooIROQ">Đào hoa đàm đoản ca - 桃花潭短歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C4%83n/author-Jkewm2VmxkXWvrVQ6hH8OQ">Phương Văn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-Ph%E1%BA%ADt-s%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-minh-l%E1%BB%A5c-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-V5fyxSCD773ZvcfNsx4dEQ">Độc “Phật sự đại minh lục” hữu cảm - 讀佛事大明錄有感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-wmykBdQiZlhullR0PPvO_Q">Trần Thánh Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%99-thu-u%E1%BB%95ng-B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ch%C3%A2u-th%E1%BB%A7-tr%C3%A1t-su%E1%BA%A5t-nh%C4%A9-khi%E1%BB%83n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%C3%BD-c%E1%BA%ADn-tr%C3%ACnh-T%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1/poem-OBlyRxjh5TCqFh5dGFYn3g">Mộ thu uổng Bùi Đạo Châu thủ trát, suất nhĩ khiển hứng, ký cận trình Tô Hoán thị ngự - 暮秋枉裴道州手札，率爾遣興，寄近呈蘇渙侍御</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ng%C6%B0-ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-OvVTBmqCMkMrRne4C_ufTQ">Ngư phủ - 漁父</a> (<a href="https://www.thi